{"tid":369450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安屢向女同事「鹹豬手」 自認「鹹濕」犯案判囚半年","createTime":"2017-08-22T10:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T10:50:30.000Z","uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3aeb238da242cb416f65720537124ccb7fec24eb","tid":369450,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:39:20.000Z","msg":"年近六旬保安員屢次向女同事施展「鹹豬手」，他在穿梭巴士、電梯及櫃位等處，先後對3名女同事摸胸、臀部及大腿。其中一名事主通知上司，並曾致電質問「鹹豬手」「你摸夠未？」，對方竟回答「未」，事主終報警求助。保安員今承認5項非禮罪，裁判官認為案情嚴重，保安員在一段時間內數度非禮同事，判監是惟一判刑選擇，判他入獄6個月。<br />\n<br />\n被告嚴金華（59歲）被指去年10月至今年1月19日於青衣5度犯案，他承認因「鹹濕」而犯案，求情指認罪而不用各事主上庭覆述尷尬經過，事後已請辭，轉任洗衣工人，望能獲得輕判。<br />\n<br />\n原來非禮人五次仲要比衝公民廣場同立法會判得輕，猿司長使唔使考慮覆核吓刑期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393c1fb4083e0b86ed0a2f75794b23dd152735f2","tid":369450,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:40:13.000Z","msg":"都幾直接"},{"pid":"fdc5fb274cfa64945410a814ad4029cc4241becf","tid":369450,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:40:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未</span></span>"},{"pid":"79e1d238168c7a5c7f9a64e5615e1350d9100e40","tid":369450,"uid":5944,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"啲同事幾大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊年紀"},{"pid":"1a1c4f0d6a066abc98c41453572813a3b5d8fee1","tid":369450,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"陳小姐終於頂唔順"},{"pid":"3f3179842c6a3ee3c9eebbb75640b547d92148f5","tid":369450,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T10:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢老勞資糾紛"}]}